{"tid":2092263,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"林夕歌詞討論區","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:07:15.000Z","uid":304089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca063134891476493761c3c04d8f38eaa60151c4","tid":2092263,"uid":304089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;Shall We Talk&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<ins>&lt;&lt;親情&gt;&gt;</ins><br />\n<br />\n&lt;明月光為何又照地堂  // 明月光為何未照地堂&gt;<br />\n<br />\n細時嫌屋企人囉嗦<br />\n<br />\n去到無得再聽既時候<br />\n<br />\n就會問<br />\n<br />\n點解 點解你瞓左覺就唔再起身再囉嗦我<br />\n<br />\n<ins>&lt;&lt;愛情&gt;&gt;</ins><br />\n<br />\n&lt;陪我講 陪我親身正視眼淚誰跌得多&gt;<br />\n<br />\n一段感情 <br />\n<br />\n總係會覺得自己付出比對方多<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟係邊一方付出得多啲 <br />\n<br />\n或者未可得到結論<br />\n<br />\n但至少我地仲有能力 去正視呢一切<br />\n<br />\n愛情 親情 <br />\n<br />\n一切一切都唔好去避<br />\n<br />\n要行動 要講 <br />\n<br />\n&lt;斜陽白趕一趟 沉默令我聽得見葉兒聲聲降&gt;<br />\n<br />\n珍惜 挽回 為時已晚 <br />\n<br />\n我所在意既人都走了<br />\n<br />\n世界變得安靜 沉默<br />\n<br />\n再無生氣<br />\n<br />\nShall we talk? <br />\n<br />\nWe shall, but we can&rsquo;t anymore."},{"pid":"c80aa8bdd79b6e04d83e46a76636ad1cf387dde1","tid":2092263,"uid":304089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca063134891476493761c3c04d8f38eaa60151c4","tid":2092263,"uid":304089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;Shall We Talk&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<ins>&lt;&lt;親情&gt;&gt;</ins><br />\n<br />\n&lt;明月光為何又照地堂  // 明月光為何未照地堂&gt;<br />\n<br />\n細時嫌屋企人囉嗦<br />\n<br />\n去到無得再聽既時候<br />\n<br />\n就會問<br />\n<br />\n點解 點解你瞓左覺就唔再起身再囉嗦我<br />\n<br />\n<ins>&lt;&lt;愛情&gt;&gt;</ins><br />\n<br />\n&lt;陪我講 陪我親身正視眼淚誰跌得多&gt;<br />\n<br />\n一段感情 <br />\n<br />\n總係會覺得自己付出比對方多<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟係邊一方付出得多啲 <br />\n<br />\n或者未可得到結論<br />\n<br />\n但至少我地仲有能力 去正視呢一切<br />\n<br />\n愛情 親情 <br />\n<br />\n一切一切都唔好去避<br />\n<br />\n要行動 要講 <br />\n<br />\n&lt;斜陽白趕一趟 沉默令我聽得見葉兒聲聲降&gt;<br />\n<br />\n珍惜 挽回 為時已晚 <br />\n<br />\n我所在意既人都走了<br />\n<br />\n世界變得安靜 沉默<br />\n<br />\n再無生氣<br />\n<br />\nShall we talk? <br />\n<br />\nWe shall, but we can&rsquo;t anymore."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"歡迎入來擺低你對林夕歌詞解讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊討論"},{"pid":"1459aeb47ff725db1a6048721a96057d799e1eaa","tid":2092263,"uid":359710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"斜陽白趕一趟 沉默令我聽得見葉兒聲聲降<br />\n呢句好似係親情，係接住「明月光 為何未照地堂」"},{"pid":"404da09072d72c288e103ba1bb9586ea984dfe31","tid":2092263,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"如果沉默太沉重 別要輕輕帶過"},{"pid":"a81f63641478b1a4d1f20c3e4de8046df762444d","tid":2092263,"uid":359710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"btw 想聽下樓主解讀不來也不去"},{"pid":"f524dceaf1d247575834176395345034f64b64a0","tid":2092263,"uid":304089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1459aeb47ff725db1a6048721a96057d799e1eaa","tid":2092263,"uid":359710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"斜陽白趕一趟 沉默令我聽得見葉兒聲聲降<br />\n呢句好似係親情，係接住「明月光 為何未照地堂」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n<br />\n不過只係我將有「明月光」嗰兩句歌詞放埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n咁 「又照地堂」同「未照地堂」兩個對比<br />\n<br />\n會強烈好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係：<br />\n<br />\n點解你又唱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解你仲唔唱....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424162c2d3244713eaa1b49446789b7b87d7e039","tid":2092263,"uid":304089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"404da09072d72c288e103ba1bb9586ea984dfe31","tid":2092263,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"如果沉默太沉重 別要輕輕帶過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"討論？"},{"pid":"28f39f63b8f0035f7806662f0ca4e7c